      "cookedHtml": "<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/wave.png?v=12\" title=\":wave:\" class=\"emoji only-emoji\" alt=\":wave:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/10000475\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Calendar Plus</a> has had a few unique updates as of late!</p>\n<p><strong>Mirror item support</strong><br />\nCalendar Plus can now display items based on mirrored dates and timelines. When you mirror <em>multiple dates</em>, Calendar Plus displays your item multiple times, instead of collapsing them into a single timeline.</p>\n<p>Additionally, mirror values can now be displayed on events, just like any other column.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/a/7/a756a23e0506881d7631bd04c29479608840cae0.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/a/7/a756a23e0506881d7631bd04c29479608840cae0.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"161\" height=\"131\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">161×131 4.36 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p><strong>Create subitems with durations</strong><br />\nJust click and drag in the calendar to add subitems to your board. Easy as!<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/a/3/a346df7333c45d2b012564f4286740c5b681b5d6.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/a/3/a346df7333c45d2b012564f4286740c5b681b5d6.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"261\" height=\"292\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">261×292 6.07 KB</span></div></a></div> <div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/a/baf5cd8760413bf871cc50d910e4975088046f7f.png\" title=\"Screen Shot 2024-11-05 at 16.28.25\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/a/baf5cd8760413bf871cc50d910e4975088046f7f.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2024-11-05 at 16.28.25\" width=\"338\" height=\"285\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screen Shot 2024-11-05 at 16.28.25</span><span class=\"informations\">584×492 14.6 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p><strong>Date picker event indicators</strong><br />\nNot sure on which day that one event is hanging out? Our date picker now sports small indicators that show which days have events on them for easy calendar navigation.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/9/c/9c688e5a72a1a664887a9efd19b9f6dc1e85f00a.png\" title=\"2024-10-28-datepicker\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/9/c/9c688e5a72a1a664887a9efd19b9f6dc1e85f00a.png\" alt=\"2024-10-28-datepicker\" width=\"339\" height=\"356\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">2024-10-28-datepicker</span><span class=\"informations\">339×356 10.8 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<hr />\n<p>That’s it for now! Find us in the marketplace: <a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/10000475\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Calendar Plus - monday.com App Marketplace</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/10000475\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/3/3/333cab32d6f1ce6a64ec86a990f00e76d4140239.png\" alt=\"10000475_2024_8_30_23_19_28_hbrcqcji\" width=\"690\" height=\"344\" /></a></p>"
